# tf_config

## TensorFlow configuration information

## Description
 TensorFlow configuration information 


## Usage
```r
 
tf_config() 
 
tf_version() 
```




## Value
 List with information on the current configuration of TensorFlow. You can determine whether TensorFlow was found using the `available` member (other members vary depending on whether `available` is `TRUE` or `FALSE`)
